00087     void execute(const std::string& str) {
00088       std::string cmd = Fs::convertCommandToUnc(str);

00092     void equivalency(const std::string& name, std::vector<string>& vFileTags)
00093     {
00094         bool bPassed = true;
00095         AffxString strFileName1;
00096         AffxString strFileName2;
00097         Verbose::out(1, "*");
00098         for(unsigned int i = 0; (i < vFileTags.size()); i++)
00099         {
00100 
00101             strFileName1 = "../../../regression-data/data/copynumber/copynumber-familial/" + name + "/" + vFileTags[i] + ".fam";
00102             strFileName2 = Fs::join(testDir , name , vFileTags[i]) + ".fam";
00103             if (!Calvin::equivalent(strFileName1, strFileName2, setIgnore, mapEpsilon, 0.0001, 0.9999989, false)) {bPassed = false;}
00104         }
00105         Verbose::out(1, "*");
00106         if (bPassed) {numPassed++;} else {numFailed++;}
00107     }

00115     void paternity()
00116     {
00117         string inputPathPrefix = "../../../regression-data/data/copynumber/copynumber-familial/paternity/input/";
00118         execute("./apt-copynumber-familial \
00119                     --index-cychp-file " + inputPathPrefix + "UPD_UC-U2a_F_01_NN_20081223.Cytogenetics_Array.REF_MODEL.cychp \
00120                     --mother-cychp-file " + inputPathPrefix + "UPD_UC-U2b_F_01_NN_20081223.Cytogenetics_Array.REF_MODEL.cychp \
00121                     --father-cychp-file " + inputPathPrefix + "UPD_UC-U2c_M_01_NN_20081223.Cytogenetics_Array.REF_MODEL.cychp \
00122                     --allele-frequency-file " + inputPathPrefix + "AlleleFrequencies_Reduced.txt \
00123                     --analysis paternity.role-validity-threshold=1000.0 \
00124                     --out-dir " + testDir + "/paternity/output \
00125                     --familial-file " + vPaternityFamFile[0] + ".fam"
00126             );
00127         equivalency("paternity/output", vPaternityFamFile);
00128     }
